data.description: Look no further! Here is a charming 3 bedroom 2 bathroom Ranch Home, nestled in Alliance Ohio. Enjoy being conveniently located near downtown with Mount Union within 1 mile and Alliance School within a 1/2 mile. Including a large backyard and a dettached garage, Enjoy your morning coffee or book in the enclosed front porch. Some updates include flooring, paint and a new hot water tank (2022). There are also hardwood floors located throughout the home. Schedule your private showing today!
